summary: Worked as part of a cross-functional and international team on Benefit Connect, a single-tenant B2B SaaS solution that powers the employee benefits experience for employers.
highlights: Spearheaded the revamp of several billing exports to improve their accuracy and ensure we met our service level agreements.
Administered our product release consumption process, ensuring the reliability of client solutions.
Assisted our talent development team in conducting interviews for college recruits.
